snippet.title: Naraka Bladepoint - Official New Weapon Trailer | E3 2021
snippet.description:
Naraka Bladepoint, one of the most played games on Steam in early access, is getting a global launch this August. A new weapon, the Chainsaw, is also being added.

#IGN #Gaming #E32021
